name: Abstract Generative Rusty Erosion Landscapes
description:
pre NFT record log...

[11-12-20]
Creating an experimental generative system using various multi-layered fractal maps with Trapcode MIR and After Effects. 

Behind the concept of this loop is the idea of erosion. The simulation of the effect of time on a fictive generated landscape. Ancient grunge aesthetics are resurfacing in the digital realm of the current millennium. 

Is there a map of meaning hidden inside the cosmic time lapse tectonics at the scale of multiple infinities perpetually emerging from the chaos of pure randomness? Or is it part of a an even bigger and more significative object like a dry, but well conserved oatmeal cookie in a bright yellow box? Only one being in the universes shall know.
